<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="strike-n">strike <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /straɪk/    美 /straɪk/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>罢工：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The workers will <strong>go on strike</strong> if the demands they put forward are turned down.
如果工人们提出的要求被拒，他们将罢工。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>stricken /'strɪkən/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>earthquake-stricken areas 
地震灾区</p></div>

<p>striker /'straɪkə(r)/ n [C]<br />
striking /'straɪkɪŋ/ adj   </p></div>